reactor.util.function

类 Tuples

  • java.lang.Object
    • reactor.util.function.Tuples
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Function

    public abstract class Tuples
extends Object
implements Function
    A Tuples is an immutable Collection of objects, each of which can be of an arbitrary type.
